pr_body:
* Added acceleration constraints to ensure smooth velocity changes
* Increased max velocity to 2. Working properly with these settings so far.

--- Tested in beta_bill env
* Added obstacle avoidance constraints
* Changed cost function. Only the first 6 positions of the robot should be closest to the path created by A*
* Added negative min velocity to go in reverse

--- Tested in run_beta_bill and run_beta_bill_walking environments ---

* Removed negative velocities
* Added on spot rotation feature
* Improved obstacle avoidance constraints

- Changed the update_costs method in the grid class (Using neighboors_8(k) instead of neighboors_16(k))
